OL,3,CThe refugees being separated under UK
OL,4,Cfamily reunion visa rules
OL,6,FITV News Correspondent Sarah Corker
OL,7,Freports on the difficulty refugees
OL,8,Fface when it comes to uniting a family
OL,9,Fin the UK
OL,11,FThe Alrfaai family are trying to build
OL,12,Fa new life together in Glasgow. After
OL,13,Fescaping the war in Syria, they were
OL,14,Fgranted asylum in Scotland three years
OL,15,Fago.
OL,17,FBut one person is missing, their
OL,18,Feldest son Mohammed, 21, is now facing
OL,19,Fdeportation to Africa.
