OL,6,F"The whole family is suffering. His
OL,7,Fmum and his sisters are all struggling
OL,8,Fto comprehend the fact that he might
OL,9,Fbe moved to Rwanda," Mohammed's father
OL,10,FHisham Alrfaai told ITV News.
OL,12,F"It doesn't make sense - the Home
OL,13,FOffice knows that his whole family's
OL,14,Fhere. So instead of reuniting him with
OL,15,Fthem, they are separating him, sending
OL,16,Fhim somewhere else. Rwanda. What does
OL,17,Fhe have to do? There is just nothing."
OL,19,FBecause he's over 18, Mohammed
OL,20,Fcouldn't get a family reunion visa to
OL,21,Fjoin his family.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/12
