OL,6,FIn desperation, he said he crossed the
OL,7,Fchannel illegally on a small boat in
OL,8,F2022.
OL,10,FSpeaking from a detention centre near
OL,11,FGatwick, he told ITV News he's close
OL,12,Fto having a mental breakdown,
OL,13,Ftraumatised by what's now happening.
