OL,6,F"They said they're going to deport me,
OL,7,Fthey said my asylum claim is not being
OL,8,Faccepted, but I don't understand
OL,9,Fwhy... they said you came here through
OL,10,Fthe backdoor, but I don't know what
OL,11,Fother door, they don't have any other
OL,12,Fdoors. I don't understand," Mohammed
OL,13,FAlrfaai said.
OL,15,FThe Alrfaai family are among thousands
OL,16,Fof families separated by immigration
OL,17,Frules.
