OL,11,FFamily reunion visas are one of the
OL,12,Fonly safe routes to the UK for
OL,13,Frefugees, but charities warn there's a
OL,14,Fbacklog of applications, many wait
OL,15,Fmuch longer than the Home Office's
OL,16,Ftarget of 12 weeks, while others
OL,17,Faren't eligible to apply at all, due
OL,18,Fto their age for example.
