OL,6,FCharities warn that a lack of safe and
OL,7,Flegal routes is pushing vulnerable
OL,8,Ffamilies into the hands of people
OL,9,Fsmuggling gangs.
OL,11,FEnver Solomon, CEO of the Refugee
OL,12,FCouncil, said: "The UK's failure to
OL,13,Fprovide adequate family reunion routes
OL,14,Fhas devastating consequences.
OL,16,F"We can all understand how utterly
OL,17,Fheart-breaking it would be to be
OL,18,Ftrapped in a different country from
OL,19,Four children or parents, with no way
OL,20,Fto reunite."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/12
