OL,6,FThe backlog of family reunion
OL,7,Fapplications in July 2023 was 11,000.
OL,8,FA joint report by the Refugee Council
OL,9,Fand Safe Passage International
OL,10,Fidentifies "serious failures and gaps"
OL,11,Fin family reunion policy in the UK.
OL,13,F'There is no safe way for children to
OL,14,Fget to the UK, so they are being
OL,15,Fforced to turn to people smugglers,'
OL,16,FRefugee Council CEO Enver Solomon told
OL,17,FITV News
OL,19,FThe report calls for five changes,
OL,20,Fincluding:
