OL,6,F"They've lost all faith in humans,
OL,7,Fespecially adults. They aren't doing
OL,8,Fso well at school, they are struggling
OL,9,Fwith a lot of mental health symptoms.
OL,10,FThey're in limbo they always had been."
OL,12,FFamily psychotherapist Philippa Kemp
OL,13,Ftold ITV News how the children she
OL,14,Fworks with have turned from 'bright'
OL,15,Fand 'hopeful' to 'depressed' with
OL,16,F'both physical and mental health
OL,17,Fissues'
