OL,6,FThe Home Office has not released data
OL,7,Fon the number of Afghans evacuated in
OL,8,Fthe UK government operation without
OL,9,Ftheir immediate family, but it
OL,10,Fconfirmed in December 2023 that it was
OL,11,Faware of at least 80 children
OL,12,Fevacuated to the UK without their
OL,13,Ffamilies.
OL,15,FFamilies were separated during the
OL,16,Fchaos of such evacuations, with those
OL,17,Fleft behind having no way to join
OL,18,Ftheir families in the UK.
