OL,6,FDefence Secretary Grant Shapps said
OL,7,Fthat the Rwanda policy is the only
OL,8,F'viable plan' to stop the boats
OL,10,FThe Home Office didn't comment on the
OL,11,Fspecifics of the family reunion visa
OL,12,Fscheme, but a spokesperson told ITV
OL,13,FNews: "We do not want people to risk
OL,14,Ftheir lives on these dangerous and
OL,15,Fillegal journeys, which is why we have
OL,16,Ftaken robust action to crack down on
OL,17,Fvile people smuggling gangs who only
OL,18,Fcare about profit.
